# 3. 未来のスターとわんだほい

Tsukasa: Okay so... Give me a moment to make sense of everything you just said. You perform at this stage?
Emu: Yup☆
Tsukasa: And I didn't pass the audition, but you invited me to join you here as a special favor?
Emu: Yup yup☆
Tsukasa: Meaning... I'm going to be working here at this dilapidated stage?!
Emu: It's not dilapidated! It has a stylish color scheme!
Tsukasa: You do realize it's not paint, it's rust, right?!
Tsukasa: But why has it been left in this state to begin with? All the other park attractions are either new or renovated and I heard they were building a brand new stage.
Mascot: The original plan was to renovate the entire park, demolishing old stages and building new ones.
Mascot: But right now, the construction of a new stage here has been put on hold.
Tsukasa: Why? And if it's going to be demolished, does it mean it's closed for now?
Emu: No, we're still doing shows! Today was Fish World Show! I played the sunfish!
Emu: There was no audience, though!
Tsukasa: What's the point then?!
Emu: But with you here, we're going to draw in crowds again! I feel it!
Tsukasa: Sigh... Now listen. I have ambitions, you know!
Emu: Oh?
Tsukasa: When I was little, I was taken to see a musical. The lead was an amazing actor.
Tsukasa: I was bedazzled! My heart was stolen! I had witnessed a true star!
Tsukasa: After that event, my mind was made up. I decided to become an illustrious star myself!
Tsukasa: But for that to happen, I must make my debut as part of a major troupe, performing in front of a great audience!
Emu: You know, there's a special trap door on the stage you can spring out of! Do you want to try it out?
Tsukasa: Were you even listening to anything I said?!
Emu: I heard lots about you at the audition!
Emu: You promised incredible shows!
Emu: That really spoke to me! I just KNEW you were the person I needed to make this stage great again!
Tsukasa: Ah, so you've been smitten with me ever since the audition? Hehe, I see. So that's how it is.
Emu: What are you writing in your notepad?
Tsukasa: I'll do this for you as a special favor. Tsu...ka...sa... Ten...ma. There, that turned out nicely.
Emu: Wow! Your writing's so cool! Is this for me? Thanks!
Tsukasa: Hahaha. Keep it safe. One day this autograph will be worth a fortune! Well then, farewell, my strange fan.
Tsukasa: Gwah!
Emu: Don't go! Let's do shows together! I promise it'll be fun!
Tsukasa: Let go of my collar, I can't...breathe!
Emu: Pleeease? Don't leave! You promised great shows!
Tsukasa: Argh... I can't...speak... Uh... Ugh... *wheeze*!
Emu: You prooomiiisseddd!
Tsukasa: If you're so keen on being in shows, just join a theater troupe!
Tsukasa: Then you can perform on proper stages, not forsaken ruins like this one!
Emu: No! It has to be here!
Emu: I made a promise! I said I'd fill all audience seats!
Tsukasa: Why'd you do that...
Emu: I want to perform here at this stage and make lots of people smile! So, please help me... Oh?
Tsukasa: Why did you stop all of a sudden?
Emu: The projector switched on all by itself... Is it broken?
Miku: <Hello everyone♪>
Miku: <An exciting show is about to begin♪ Are you ready?>
Tsukasa: That's a Hatsune Miku hologram. I didn't know she was this park's mascot character.
Emu: She isn't. Our mascot is Phenny the Phoenix Penguin.
Tsukasa: Then what is this?
Miku: <It seems everyone's ready to start! Allow me to take you on a fun-filled adventure in a wonderful SEKAI!>
Emu: She disappeared! What was that about?
Tsukasa: How would I know?
Tsukasa: Sigh... This day's just been one thing after another. I don't have the energy for this.
Tsukasa: No offense, but I'm going to phone HR and officially resign.
Emu: Whaaat?! No, please, listen—
Tsukasa: I've listened enough! Where did I save that number...
Tsukasa: What's this? It says “Untitled”?
Emu: What's that? A song?
Tsukasa: Hey, give me some space!
Emu: I wanna hear it♪ Tap!
Tsukasa: Argh! Hands off my phone! What if it's one of those scams where they lock your phone with a virus if you don't pay up or something?!
Tsukasa: What the heck? My phone's flashing! Don't tell me it really was some scammer's virus?!
Emu: Eek! I can't see!
Tsukasa: What was that... Huh, what's this? Where am I?!
Tsukasa: How did I get here? I can't see Emu anywhere either.
???: .....
Tsukasa: Uh... I know you're there. Show yourself!
???: It's Mikudayo☆
Tsukasa: Aaaaaaaargh! Wh-What on earth?!
